We are committed to ensuring the safety and protection of children. The Jain Dharma app does not host or allow user-generated content, comments, chat, or any media uploads. This application is informational and offers devotional content (Aarti, Chalisa, Mantras) based on Jain philosophy.

We do not tolerate or permit any form of child sexual abuse or exploitation (CSAE). If we become aware of any such content or behavior, we will take immediate action, including reporting it to the appropriate authorities.

If you believe our app is being misused, please contact us at: honeyjain157@gmail.com
